</span> of DPS</div><div>High = Stats that help round out other aspects of play, defense and survivability are top priority</div><div>Moderate = Stats that have a benefical effect that is sometimes noticable, sometimes benefical</div><div>Low = stats that have very very rare use</div><div>None = no benefit gained from stat.</div><div></div>
