			>
			<DIV>Giving numbers for ease of reading 1-10</DIV>
<DIV>CLASS: Monk<BR>&nbsp;<BR>HP: 10 very important. Dead monks do no damage.<BR>Mana: N/A<BR>Endurance: 8 Important. <BR>AC: 7<BR>&nbsp;<BR>HP Regen: 3 More important at the lower levels but at high levels its useless unless its&nbsp; really high.<BR>Mana Regen: N/A<BR>Endurance Regen: 8 Need more End regen things in game, items AA whatever.<BR>&nbsp;<BR>Strength: 4 Diminishing returns on this skill make it less usefull they higher it gets.<BR>Stamina: 10<BR>Agility: 7 Diminishing returns on this skill make it less usefull they higher it gets.<BR>Dexterity: 7 Diminishing returns on this skill make it less usefull they higher it gets.<BR>Charisma: 1 Only useful for selling to NPC vendors. Should have some secondary use in future?<BR>Intelligence: 1 Only useful for increasing trade skills.<BR>Wisdom: 1 Only useful for increasing trade skills.</DIV>
<DIV>Cold Resist: 8<BR>Disease Resist: 8<BR>Poison Resist: 8<BR>Magic Resist: 9 <BR>Fire Resist: 8</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Noticing high end items for monks are starting to have less Dexterity and Magic resistance. Why?<BR>&nbsp;<BR>Attack: 10 <BR>Delay: 10<BR>Damage: 10<BR>Range: 5<BR>Haste: 10 </DIV>
<DIV>We are a melee DPS class.<BR>&nbsp;<BR>Combat Effects: 8<BR>Shielding: 8<BR>Stun Resist: 8<BR>Strikethrough: 9<BR>Spell Shield: 7<BR>Avoidance: 8<BR>Accuracy: 9<BR>DOT Shielding: 6<BR>&nbsp;<BR>Skill Mods: 8<BR>Click Effects: 10 Having no spells click effects really help utility.<BR>Proc Effects: 10<BR>Worn Effects: 9<BR>Focus Effects: 8 Need more and better focus effects for melee abilities.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Added Skills Stats:</DIV>
<DIV>Ferocity: 10<BR>Cleave: 10 </DIV>
<DIV>Mend: 10</DIV>
<DIV>Feign Death: 10</DIV>
<DIV>Disarm: 0 Really need to make this useful somehow. Add short duration effect that lowers attack.</DIV>
<DIV>Intimidation: 0 Really need to make this useful without creating trains. Make the mob cower in fear for a short duration rather than run all over hell. Makes it more vulnerable to attacks.</DIV>
<DIV>Begging: 0 No use in game.</DIV>
<DIV>Language Skills: 0 Very little use in game.</DIV>
<DIV><BR>&nbsp;</DIV>
