			<DIV>CLASS: Monk
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP: Most Important<BR>Mana: N/A<BR>Endurance: We use it, but I wouldnt put a +100 END aug on my stuff.<BR>AC: Important to me since the changes to Return over softcap for monks&nbsp; </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP Regen: Useful for soloing<BR>Mana Regen: N/A<BR>Endurance Regen: Would be nice to have some of this.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Strength: Stat #2<BR>Stamina: Stat #1<BR>Agility: Stat #3(also toughest to raise of the 4 melee stats)<BR>Dexterity: stat #4<BR>Charisma: useless over 120<BR>Intelligence: useless<BR>Wisdom: useless</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Cold Resist: Resists is good<BR>Disease Resist: Resists is good<BR>Poison Resist: Resists is good<BR>Magic Resist: Monk gear seems to be lacking this one<BR>Fire Resist: Resists is good</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Attack: Not hard to raise to cap, very useful stat if you take one item.<BR>Delay: lower the better =) Cept 2Handers, most prefer the magic number of 28<BR>Damage: Higher the better...<BR>Range:&nbsp;200 on pulling items helps avoiding getting too close for Phantom Cry to be useful.</DIV>
<DIV>Haste: Higher the better</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Combat Effects: More please.&nbsp; <BR>Shielding: Love this stat.&nbsp; <BR>Stun Resist: Always nice to shake off the stun effect<BR>Strikethrough: Useful in group situations when monks are more likely to be in front of a mob than on a raid situation.<BR>Spell Shield: Lessens AE damage, gotta love that.<BR>Avoidance: my favorite of the PoTime special stats<BR>Accuracy: From parses it doesnt seem to help as much as it says, but wouldnt turn an item down&nbsp;with Accuracy<BR>DOT Shielding: might be the least useful for my tastes.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Skill Mods: Are there any Skill Mod Block items post Time Tunic?<BR>Click Effects: always nice either with ATK bonuses, Resists, etc...<BR>Proc Effects: Prefer Lifetaps.<BR>Worn Effects: Cleave, Fero, Dodge, Block, love em all.&nbsp; Probably Fero the most as monks are always smacking the mob and more double attk means more dmg.<BR>Focus Effects: Monks have what, 2 focus effects, one on epic 1.5, another on 2.0(same basic effect, but different level of focus)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Appearance: would like to take Generic archetype armor and tune it into the robe or chest strap look.&nbsp; Gloves/wrist items&nbsp;that look like hand wraps.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Would also like more items like the Padded Tigerskin Gloves from PoTime, leather appearance item useable by all melee classes....That are competetive with today's stats.</DIV></DIV>	
