		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			CLASS: Monk
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div>HP: Very important, due to OT'ing, dealing with aoes at raids and tanking for exp.<br>Mana: N/A<br>Endurance: Useful, though unless some decent dics come along that use more, I have plenty of end at approx 11k, regen after death is an issue.<br>AC: I enjoy high ac, though I would not go out of my way to get it.<br> </div>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div>HP Regen: The cap needs to be raised, regen on items is low, never been capped in 6 years.<br>Mana Regen: N/A<br>Endurance Regen: I do not think end regen is needed at this time, discs/end were supposed to be balanced and appear to be so.<br> </div>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div>Strength: Easily maxed for me.<br>Stamina: Easily maxed.<br>Agility: Moderately hard to max.<br>Dexterity: Moderately hard to maxed.<br>Charisma: Very hard to max, would enjoy having mroe cha on items for vendor purchases and DI firing (If cha affects this).<br>Intelligence: N/A<br>Wisdom: N/A<br> </div>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div>Cold Resist: Average<br>Disease Resist: Pretty hard to max.<br>Poison Resist: Moderately hard to max.<br>Magic Resist: Very hard if not possible to max, more MR please.<br>Fire Resist: Monks best resists (innate FR)<br> </div>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div>Attack: Easy to max.<br>Delay: Important<br>Damage: Extremely important<br>Range: Nice to have<br> </div>
<div>Haste: can't live without.<br> </div>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div>Combat Effects: <br>Shielding: 3rd importance to me.<br>Stun Resist: average<br>Strikethrough: Does little for the mods and AAs bought. <br>Spell Shield: hard to max<br>Avoidance: Easy to max<br>Accuracy:&nbsp; Very hard to max<br>DOT Shielding: impossile to max<br> </div>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
Skill Mods: <br>Click Effects: 3<br>Proc Effects: 2<br>Worn Effects: 1<br>Focus Effects: 4<br> <div></div>	
