<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Attack: 2 (Paladin dps is garbage, so I don't really bother)<BR>Delay: 4 (Higher is better)<BR>Damage: 4 (Higher is obvoiusly better)<BR>Range: 0 (Knight archery's on the level of wizard melee damage. Haven't touched a bow in over a year)</DIV>
<DIV>Haste: 5 (not a lot of haste options. Very valuable)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Combat Effects: 3 (Since we don't need proc aggro, not very relevant. Fun for lifetaps and wave heal procs though)<BR>Shielding: 5 (yes please)<BR>Stun Resist: 4 (Getting stunned is annoying. Especially for 12 seconds)<BR>Strikethrough: 2 (Dps. /snicker)<BR>Spell Shield: 4 (Not a lot around on gear we use, and we need it)<BR>Avoidance: 5 (yes please)<BR>Accuracy: 2 (Haha)<BR>DOT Shielding: 4 (EXTREMELY rare. I don't even bother looking at it since there's basically none on tank gear)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Skill Mods: (No idea if this does anything. There's not a single mod on any piece of gear I've ever owned)<BR>Click Effects: 4 (Spell Clickies for non casters/priests with reasonable cast times would be very nice. We have vish shoulders, por tier1, por tier2 bp. Everything else I've found is too stupidly long cast time to matter. (Hello ornate gear))<BR>Proc Effects: 5 (More wave heal procs. More more more! Damage/aggro procs = not needed though)<BR>Worn Effects: </DIV>
<DIV>Improved Parry: 5</DIV>
<DIV>Improved Dodge:5</DIV>
<DIV>Faerune:&nbsp;3 (Kind of rare, very nice for humans who're night blind)</DIV>
<DIV>DPS ones are a matter of choice. I don't care about 'em<BR>Focus Effects: </DIV>
