			>
			<DIV></DIV>
<P>Grendellkill, Povar, 70 Wizard (havn't seen one post), Anguish + geared. High end raid guild. 835 AAs.</P>
<P>1. Stat not listed might be most important to Wizards : Spell Casting Subtlety. We have basically been relegated into DPS and AE TLing for utility, neither of which we can do dead. The only item I have that has any type of agro mitigation is my 2.0. I have all the agro affecting AAs, but I can get agro quickly. Very quickly. </P>
<P>2. Damage Foci. Very Important for a Wiz, but the best items have shared classes on them. Really sucks to bid on an item with the best Fire Damage Focus available to you, and be outbid by a Cleric.&nbsp; Maybe some uber Damage mods that are Wiz only?</P>
<P>3. All the other stuff that has been helpfull IE: Avoidance, DoT sheilding, Spellsheilding, I have been able to max in the course of upgrading gear. </P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
