<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
Reply <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=DevCorner&message.id=12838#M12838">145</a> of 370
</span>

			<br><img src="/i/p.gif" width=1 height=6><br>
			<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
			
					Viewed 1427 times<br>
					
			</span>
			
		</td>
		
		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<div>CLASS: RANGER
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div>HP:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Very critical<br>Mana:&nbsp;&nbsp; Good to have<br>Endurance:&nbsp; matters naught<br>AC:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Very good<br> </div>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div>HP Regen:&nbsp;&nbsp; Moderately useful<br>Mana Regen:&nbsp; Very useful (I'm making a lot of compromises to keep myself maxed)<br>Endurance Regen: There is such a thing?&nbsp; Meh.&nbsp; Don't care.<br> </div>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div>Strength:&nbsp;&nbsp; n/a<br>Stamina:&nbsp; n/a<br>Agility:&nbsp; n/a<br>Dexterity:&nbsp; n/a<br>Charisma:&nbsp; n/a<br>Intelligence:&nbsp; n/a<br>Wisdom: n/a<br> </div>
<div><br>Note:&nbsp; Base stats capped so long ago, it doesn't matter.&nbsp; Raise the caps 100 points and ask me again.) <br><br></div>
<div>Cold Resist:&nbsp; Moderately important<br>Disease Resist: Moderately important<br>Poison Resist: Moderately important<br>Magic Resist: Moderately important<br>Fire Resist: Moderately important </div>
<div>&nbsp;<br>Note:&nbsp; There's too many encounters where the really nasty effects are -1000 to resists, so it doesn't matter.&nbsp; We reserve Infusion just for the one or two fights where resists matter most.<br><br></div>
<div>Attack:&nbsp;&nbsp; Moderately important.&nbsp; I think I'm over the limit, but I can boost the limit more than I have, so I'd take it.<br>Delay:&nbsp;&nbsp; There's trade-offs here.&nbsp; Too little delay seems to create more agro.&nbsp; But the ratio is the critical stat.<br>Damage:&nbsp; Love it.&nbsp; Live by it.<br>Range:&nbsp; This sets rangers apart from everyone else.&nbsp; They have good bows with decent ratios, but we have the long range arrows with the great damage.<br> </div>
<div>Haste:&nbsp; Gotta have it, but only one matters.&nbsp; Each expansion seems to move the haste to a different slot, making the upgrade path complicated and troubling.<br> </div>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div>Combat Effects: Great to have<br>Shielding:&nbsp; Haven't seen a noticable impact.<br>Stun Resist: Haven't seen a noticable impact.<br>Strikethrough: I like it, but I've been told the effect is too small to be measurable.<br>Spell Shield: Haven't seen a noticable impact.<br>Avoidance: Haven't seen a noticable impact.<br>Accuracy: Haven't seen a noticable impact, BUT I really like the sound of it.<br>DOT Shielding:&nbsp; Haven't seen a noticable impact. </div>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
Skill Mods:&nbsp; Some of the more "odd" skill mods would get my attention.&nbsp; There's time when I could really use that taunt mod, or channeling, or kick. <br>Click Effects: Critically important.&nbsp; This is what makes an item highly coveted and keeps it around long after it's no longer worth wearing.&nbsp; I did my 1.5 primarilly for the click effect, even sacrificing DPS for it, but I would have done it sooner if I could have clicked it from inventory.<br>Proc Effects: Important, BUT be careful.&nbsp; Rangers walk a fine line between all-out DPS and agro-magnet.&nbsp; If I saw a weapon with a 1200dd proc, I'd have to say no.&nbsp; Now, if it had 1200dd AND agro reduction, I'd be excited.&nbsp; <br>Worn Effects:  Can I get a Deadly Kick effect?&nbsp; That would be too cool.&nbsp; I'm a long way from the AA's to replace Faerune, so it's still very important to me that I have it.<br>Focus Effects: VERY, VERY important.&nbsp; I think if you categorized the augs I'm using, this would be the first or second biggest category.<br><br><br>You've left out AUG SLOTS.&nbsp; I switched to the (**SMURF**, broken, annoying) Cloak of the Spirit Tracker partly because of the type 7 aug slot.&nbsp; If you made some items with both type 7 and type 8, that would ROCK.<br><br></div>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							--
Negotiations failed.  Rezz me and let's kill them.
							</div>
								
		</td></tr>
		<tr>
		
